oai_dc:dc.dc:title: View of Knoxville, TN, 1865. Part 4 of 4.
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: T.M. Schleier
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: View of Knoxville, TN, 1865. Taken by T.M. Schleier from a hill on the South Knoxville side of the river. Fort Sanders is on the extreme left of Part 1 and Reservoir Hill is on the extreme right of Part 4. Part 4 of 4. Slight overlap on scans.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Cityscapes; Panoramic photographs;
